name: New Livery - Cargolux 747-4R7F [LX-SCV] Evening Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
An extra special catch, Cargolux in daylight for once with their 747-400 (in the new livery to boot)! Here we have CV775, a regular service into YYC, but almost always between the ungodly hours of 1-5 in the morning. First time seeing their 744 in the 748 livery too. Enjoy this special catch with ATC!

Thanks for watching!
